    "Long before humans, the Goddess of Prosperity gave birth to her first child — Hastar. He was greedy beyond measure. He desired all the gold... and all the food... and everything that was never meant to be his." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Long before humans, the Goddess of Prosperity gave birth to her first child — Hastar. He was greedy beyond measure. He desired all the gold... and all the food... and everything that was never meant to be his."
          }
        },
        "es-419" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Mucho antes de los humanos, la Diosa de la Prosperidad dio a luz a su primer hijo: Hastar. Era codicioso sin medida. Deseaba todo el oro... y toda la comida... y todo lo que nunca debió ser suyo."
          }
        }
      }
    },
